                    <h3 style="text-align: center; margin-top: 5%">About Us</h3>
                    <p style="text-align:justify; margin-left: 50px">The Government of Punjab is pleased to announce the launch of the “Punjab Health Facility Portal” where all public and private health facilities are invited to self-report on the various health services they provide in their respective health facilities. This information will be made available to citizens through this portal to allow them to make more informed choices of what health services they can access from where. The information will help the Punjab Government to identify gaps and strengthen health services delivery and improve citizen satisfaction.
                        </br></br>We request you to partner with the State to make this important venture a resounding success. For this, healthcare providers are requested to self-register by clicking on “Register Facility/Login” button. Please note this portal will be dynamic and allow for changes to be made as they take place in future. Users of health facilities are requested to provide feedback.
                        </br></br>We hope that citizens of state find this portal useful and provide feedback regarding services.</p>
